name: scroll
description:
VJ loop created for my live VJ set.
1280x720px. 29s loop.

All my VJ loops are created based on the concept of Visual Music, where the images follow formal aspects of music like rhythm, tempo, melody, etc. The animations are always related to a specific song and dialogue with it as an additional instrument, in order to create a unified audiovisual piece.

More information about my VJ work at http://vj.1mpar.com
